---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import labImg from '../assets/photos/lab.png';
---

<header
  class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-start bg-navy-600 overflow-hidden"
  aria-labelledby="hero-heading"
>
  <!-- Diagonal-stripe pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.055]" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg width="100%" height="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <defs>
        <pattern id="diagonals" width="20" height="20" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse" patternTransform="rotate(45)">
          <line x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="20" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.6"/>
        </pattern>
      </defs>
      <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#diagonals)" />
    </svg>
  </div>

  <!-- Central Glow -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full h-full max-w-5xl max-h-5xl bg-em-400/10 blur-[140px] rounded-full pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="hero-parallax relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 pt-32 lg:py-32 w-full">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center lg:items-start">
      
      <!-- Left: Content (Staggered lower on desktop) -->
      <div class="text-center lg:text-left lg:mt-20">
        <!-- Eyebrow -->
        <p
          class="text-em-400 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6 opacity-0 animate-[fadeIn_0.6s_cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1)_0.1s_forwards]"
        >
          Strategiczne przywództwo IVD
        </p>

        <!-- H1 -->
        <h1
          id="hero-heading"
          class="font-serif text-[clamp(3rem,5vw+0.5rem,5rem)] font-bold text-white leading-[1.2] tracking-tight mb-8 opacity-0 animate-[fadeUp_0.8s_cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1)_0.2s_forwards]"
        >
          <span class="sr-only">Sebastian Sośniak — </span><span class="text-em-400">25 lat</span> w IVD.<br/>
          Od diagnostyki do biznesu.
        </h1>

        <!-- Name tag -->
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-white/[0.05] border border-white/10 rounded-full px-6 py-2 mb-6 opacity-0 animate-[fadeIn_0.6s_cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1)_0.35s_forwards]"
        >
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-em-400" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="text-white/90 text-base font-medium tracking-wide">Sebastian Sośniak</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Subtitle -->
        <div
          class="text-slate-300/90 text-lg sm:text-xl leading-[1.85] mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 opacity-0 animate-[fadeUp_0.7s_cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1)_0.5s_forwards] space-y-5"
        >
          <p>Zaczynałem przy analizatorach, skończyłem z P&amp;L. Dzięki temu widzę ten rynek inaczej
          niż większość i to jest moja realna przewaga.</p>
          <p>Laboratoria, producenci, zespoły handlowe, znam każdą z tych perspektyw od środka.
          Jeśli szukasz kogoś, kto rozumie ten biznes jako manager, doradca lub partner
          do rozmowy strategii, odezwij się.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA buttons -->
        <div
          class="flex flex-wrap justify-center lg:justify-start gap-4 opacity-0 animate-[fadeUp_0.6s_cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1)_0.65s_forwards]"
        >
          <a href="/cv-sebastian-sosniak.pdf" download="CV_Sebastian_Sosniak.pdf" class="btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4" aria-label="Pobierz CV Sebastian Sośniak (PDF)">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4" />
            </svg>
            Pobierz CV
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sebastiansosniak/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="btn-linkedin text-lg px-8 py-4"
            aria-label="Profil LinkedIn Sebastian Sośniak (otworzy się w nowej karcie)"
          >
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
            </svg>
            LinkedIn
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats strip -->
        <div
          class="mt-14 pt-10 border-t border-white/10 grid grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 opacity-0 animate-[fadeIn_0.8s_cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1)_0.8s_forwards]"
          aria-label="Kluczowe liczby"
        >
          {
            [
              { count: 25, suffix: '+', label: 'Lat w branży IVD' },
              { count: 7,  suffix: '',  label: 'Krajów regionu EMEA' },
              { count: 110, suffix: '%', label: 'Realizacja targetów' },
            ].map((stat) => (
              <div>
                <p
                  class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-em-400 tabular-nums"
                  data-count={stat.count}
                  data-suffix={stat.suffix}
                >
                  {stat.count}{stat.suffix}
                </p>
                <p class="text-white/60 text-[10px] sm:text-xs mt-2 leading-snug uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold">{stat.label}</p>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Lab Image (Hidden on mobile, high on desktop) -->
      <div class="hidden lg:mt-36 lg:block relative opacity-0 animate-[fadeIn_1s_cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1)_0.4s_forwards]">
        <!-- Decorative frame -->
        <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-24 h-24 border-t-2 border-l-2 border-em-400/30 rounded-tl-2xl -z-10"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-32 h-32 border-b-2 border-r-2 border-em-400/30 rounded-br-2xl -z-10"></div>
        
        <div class="relative aspect-[4/3] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10 shadow-2xl shadow-navy-900/50">
          <Image 
            src={labImg} 
            alt="Sebastian Sośniak w laboratorium diagnostycznym" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale-[0.1] hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700 scale-105 hover:scale-100"
            loading="eager"
          />
          <!-- Subtle overlay -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-navy-900/40 to-transparent"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Floating Badge -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-4 shadow-xl hidden xl:block">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-em-50 flex items-center justify-center text-em-500">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0113.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 00-9-9z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider font-bold text-slate-400">Ekspercka wiedza</p>
              <p class="text-sm font-bold text-navy-600 leading-none">Praktyka laboratoryjna</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<script>
  const parallaxEl = document.querySelector<HTMLElement>('.hero-parallax');
  if (
    parallaxEl &&
    !window.matchMedia('(prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)').matches
  ) {
    const hero = parallaxEl.closest('header') as HTMLElement;
    window.addEventListener(
      'scroll',
      () => {
        const y = window.scrollY;
        const limit = hero.offsetHeight * 1.3;
        if (y < limit) {
          parallaxEl.style.transform = `translateY(${y * 0.12}px)`;
        } else {
          parallaxEl.style.transform = '';
        }
      },
      { passive: true }
    );
  }
</script>
